  "title": "Call Agent - 6 months contract",
  "description": "<ul><li>Work Location - Central Region</li><li>Working Hours - Mon to Thurs 8.30am - 6pm, Fri 8.30am - 5.30pm</li><li>Monthly Salary - up to $2500 per month</li><li>6 Months Contract, Govt Agencies</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform reminder outbound calls to directors of companies</li><li>Send follow-up emails to the directors whom we are unable to contact via call</li><li>Reply to directors’ queries where applicable</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>A keen desire to learn new things, are self-driven and are team players</li><li>Relevant service delivery experience such as in customer service, telemarketing, or call centres (preferred)</li><li>Excel skills are required</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, kindly email your resume to: <strong>zuli.ng@tg-hr.com</strong></p><p><strong>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
